{
  "stem": "935.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now the Dutch were saying, they mean all-- the Poles, the Czech, the Austrians-- they don't mean us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why us?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First of all, as I said, there is no a-- there was no anti-Semitism there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This also makes a great-- the Dutch Jews didn't start riot-- the Dutch people didn't start rioting and say, dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Utrecht, I was a few months until the producer I had originally left Vienna with got permission for me to come to Amsterdam-- the mission was given from the Dutch police president in Amsterdam -- to work in a theatre.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had the work papers and the papers that I could stay there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when I came to Amsterdam, which was the most fascinating of all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there, nobody knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, this was really life as usual.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was full of German immigrants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they all did fabulously well, because they had already left-- most of them-- in '33.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had talked now already about '40-- 1940, late 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at first I worked at the Beatrix Theatre-- like the name Beatrix, B-E-A-T-R-I-X, like one-- you know, the queen's, of the queen's daughters.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, later on, I changed to the same-- it was in the same street, just a few houses away was another theatre, which was the Hollandsche Schouwburg.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hollandsche Schouwburg-- Hollandsche is Dutch, Schouwburg is the Dutch name for theatre.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
